 月 29 日告知产生 1.7 万元费用，崔某对该费用产生质疑，双方未谈拢维修费用。目前，区交通、市场监管和公安等部门已组成联合调查组，并积极对接吉安市新干县有关部门深入调查此事，依法依规进行处理，维护公民的合法权益，坚决维护公平公正的法治化营商环境。货车司机遭遇 1.7 万元修车？官方通报：已组成联合调查组"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c84dd61819e0a22d1a9b6ae5a323103c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "158 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651336890"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjOvr/JOH49MsEAMaCTEwNzAxOTMzNiCs866wBjAAOHBABXIJNjUxMzM2ODkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1712207964.510388", "card_id": "Q_607829458", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 248}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么米哈游一直不出二次元高人气人设「打一拳能嘤嘤嘤哭半天的软弱性格女角色」并且实装在原神或者崩铁里？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "见过这么多女性人设最戳我的就是海贼王里的白星了，真希望米哈游能有类似角色啊。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ec31c032de2d63eb8a0a17efaf1b1091_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "79 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/607829458"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjOvr/JOH49MsEAMaCDk3MzUzODgxIJn0yqQGMAA4wgJABnIJNjA3ODI5NDU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1712207964.510803", "card_id": "Q_651205680", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "作为打工人，最近每天都很累，过的力不从心，但家人清明打电话问我近况让我回家，我该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3187cd542c77aa0158c85d8a04f3e964_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_are